snippet.title: Once Upon a Jester - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Once Upon a Jester is available now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/once-upon-a-jester-switch/

Travel the kingdom as Jester with his best friend Sok to improvise theater shows and perform on stages far and wide. Sing your hearts out, crack jokes and impress audiences to become the stars of the famous Royal Theatrical Spectacle!

#OnceUponAJester #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
